Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.90,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum Balloon!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.37,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been had...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.09,0:02:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our treasure is gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.94,0:02:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're getting away! After them!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.57,0:02:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lt. Commander!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.15,0:02:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,These are shallow waters, and we \Nhave to go through the shore reef,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so all this smoke is dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.16,0:03:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that! And I don't care!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.80,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they make it onto the ocean outside?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.12,0:03:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wind up the laughingstock \Nand shame of the entire Navy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.84,0:03:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We... the Navarone Fortress... will?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.32,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! \NThose damn Navy bigwigs'll start arguing again
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.03,0:03:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,about destroying some useless hedgehog of a fortress
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.49,0:03:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that can't even capture a \Nsingle bug that snuck inside!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.40,0:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You! As a marine of the Navarone Fortress, \Ncan you tolerate that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.86,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, all warships!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.08,0:03:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Full speed ahead! Pass through the Sea Gate!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.71,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the outside ocean! \NWe can get out if we go straight ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we can't leave!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.76,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.47,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the ship back! Turn it around! Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.76,0:04:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going back into the fortress! \NThe Navy stole all our gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.69,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you insane, Nami?! \NWe almost died trying to get this far!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.29,0:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sane!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we do make it out, \Nthere's no point without the gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.37,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When money is involved, \Nshe can be strangely persuasive...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I love that side of Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.00,0:04:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But we made that huge hole! \NWhy can't we just leave now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we pirates, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.46,0:04:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.18,0:04:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think pirates leaving gold behind is shameful?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.93,0:04:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Then it's decided!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.89,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right rudder, full! Make a U-turn \Nand take us back into the fortress!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.91,0:04:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! As you wish, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right rudder, full!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.15,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,U-turn!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, you guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be reckless!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, that's it! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.18,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound the alarm bell! Louder!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.14,0:05:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't see a thing in this smoke! \NBe sure not to hit any fellow ships!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.94,0:05:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.36,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.53,0:05:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind chimes?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.32,0:05:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,These are alarm bells for signaling \Nyour location to other ships in fog!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.12,0:05:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! One's coming straight at us!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.00,0:05:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? Is that good enough, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.21,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Left rudder, full!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.00,0:06:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to change course or we'll crash!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna crash!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.24,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We almost wound up in pieces \Nwithout ever seeing the gold again...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How are things up ahead?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.09,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots more wind chimes than before!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.93,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one... two... no, even more warships coming from the smoke!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.48,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! What'll it be? \NLeft or right rudder?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,More left!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.32,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta get out of this smoke!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.86,0:07:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do what she says! \NShe's the best navigator in the world!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna crash for sure this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, God...!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going straight now!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.44,0:07:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get out of this dangerous \Nsmoke as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna spot us, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.74,0:07:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! \NWe'll be sitting ducks once we leave the smoke!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.96,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get blasted and wind up at the bottom of the ocean!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to play it by ear!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.88,0:08:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Navigator...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.24,0:08:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I did some research in the reference room...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.20,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,this fortress actually used to house many more people and warships.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.06,0:08:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, Robin! \NThis is no time for old stories!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.40,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was military downsizing. \NThey've really fallen into decline since.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.83,0:08:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems there are many unused docks in this port.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Unused docks...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! That's some nice info, Robin!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.70,0:08:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! We're gonna hide the \NGoing Merry in an old dock!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! And where exactly is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow my orders!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.73,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the cannoneers at the waterway!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask if the Straw Hat ship passed through!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.49,0:09:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, cannoneers! \NThis is Drake's flagship!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen the Straw Hats' ship?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.37,0:09:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, no other ships have \Npassed through the Sea Gate yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you disappear to, pirates?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.38,0:09:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you managed to \Nsneak past the cannoneers
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.26,0:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and vanish beyond the horizon in that short period of time?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.17,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost sight of the pirate ship \Nonce it entered the outer waters!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost as if they magically turned invisible!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.60,0:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.45,0:09:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, good work. Come on back for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We can talk leisurely about our forthcoming plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.33,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't try to escape.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.38,0:10:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with their dreams still in this fortress...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.56,0:10:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Unhand me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.86,0:10:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna be court-martialed for insulting a superior officer?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that? He's gonna court-martial us!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead! Be our guest!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.74,0:10:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You two! Let that man go!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Major!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you so!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.00,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Major Shepherd, special inspector for Navy Command!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.84,0:10:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say the Straw Hats are right around here...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.22,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to use them a little more.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.22,0:11:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I guess I'll wait for them to come out on their own.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.56,0:11:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Straw Hat pirates \Nhave us working like crazy...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.22,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for some good, energizing grub, \Nthen it's back to searching.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?! \NThis isn't like this morning's food!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.53,0:11:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'd never had anything like it before!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.75,0:11:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't be skimpin'! \NGive us some grub like this morning's!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us good food! Give us good food!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.46,0:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica-{\i1}san{\i0}! \NThe soldiers are complaining about their meals!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.01,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us good food! Give us good food!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.30,0:11:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let us use those recipes!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.60,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where has your pride as \Ncooks of Navarone gone?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.70,0:11:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that he was a pirate, \Nbut he was still an excellent cook
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.40,0:11:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,who made food for the famished \Nsoldiers who came here to eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.57,0:12:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! All these men want to be revitalized by eating his food!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make a decision! Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.41,0:12:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Jessica-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.30,0:12:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.47,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}will{\i0} make our own cooking
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.88,0:12:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that's every bit as delicious and replenishing as his!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.03,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But for today, we'll abandon our \Ncheap pride and borrow his recipes!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.98,0:12:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that he wasn't a pirate \Nin the kitchen... he was a cook.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.03,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's most important of all is \Nsatisfying the people eating!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you standing around for?! \NThose men are waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.83,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now, Nami?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.21,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not too late yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}should{\i0} go back to the \Ngate and get onto the ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.88,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! These guys mean business!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.84,0:13:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame about the gold, \Nbut our lives are more important!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.31,0:13:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We need the gold! \NBut I'm hungry! Sanji! Food!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.49,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look for some food and make you somethin'.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.69,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The storeroom is empty.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.40,0:13:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be something left somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.61,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think it's okay to \Nescape without getting the gold?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.95,0:13:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a pity. \NPirate treasure is {\i1}always{\i0} divided up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.79,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And given all that gold, we'd each have gotten so much money!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Divided up?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.72,0:13:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.68,0:13:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this! \NI'm gonna buy me a bronze statue!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.56,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Can we buy books?! \NI want the latest medical books!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.23,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to study all sorts of medical techniques I don't know about!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.19,0:13:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,New pots and frying pans, \Nplus silverware and giant mousetraps...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves a crapload left over!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I could drink all I want!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.49,0:14:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,First, my stash will be 80%!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.73,0:14:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously! \NYou can't just openly have a secret stash!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.88,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By "stash," I mean money \Nsaved up to repair the ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship? You mean Merry?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.81,0:14:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The Going Merry is what \Nbrought us where we are now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.81,0:14:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it {\i1}has{\i0} given us a ride on the seas \Never since my East Blue village...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.44,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a slightly older model, \Nbut I personally designed it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.69,0:14:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A carvel-make caravel, with lateen \Nsails and a central stern rudder...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.87,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Going Merry!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on already.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.17,0:14:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.88,0:15:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to be captain, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be dumb! {\i1}I'm{\i0} the captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.14,0:15:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We've made so many memories with this ship...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of leaving this island!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... going now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.81,0:15:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be back someday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.48,0:16:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was with us when we crossed Reverse Mountain
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and burst onto the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.61,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be real!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.78,0:16:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The ocean really is flowing up it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going into the clouds!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.47,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it! This is the greatest sea in the world! \NThe Grand Line!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.14,0:16:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The One Piece is up ahead, somewhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.44,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the sky islands...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this ship's navigator?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You are, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.87,0:16:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, men! Do what Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} says!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.04,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're flying!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.84,0:17:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! The ship is flying!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! You're wonderful!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.03,0:17:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I like you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.64,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I even risked my life to protect it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.89,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't harm the ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then someone fixed the ship for us...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.76,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I really saw it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.18,0:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think about it, \Nthis ship's been through a lot!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.86,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done so much for us, but now it's all beat up.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea! The Going Merry's Great Repair!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.92,0:18:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then. \NSince we don't know how much it'll cost,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.15,0:18:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll hold off on dividing up the \Ntreasure when we get it back.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.15,0:18:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They took most of the food, \Nbut not the stuff in the fridge.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dig in.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.71,0:18:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Usopp's cheap repairs {\i1}are{\i0} just about at their limit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.78,0:18:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know that I'm a sniper!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.76,0:18:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But yeah, Mechao-{\i1}san{\i0} said the same thing... \Nthat it needs real repairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.23,0:18:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. \NWe should go to a real shipbuilding dock
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.10,0:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and have real shipwrights fix it for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people better than you at fixing ships, Usopp?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.58,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you gotta take extra good care,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.07,0:18:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,or you'll wind up paying for it later!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, it's decided!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.41,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get a shipwright in our crew!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our journey is far from over!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.79,0:19:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We need those skills anyway...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.05,0:19:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And Merry is our home! Our life!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.88,0:19:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find a shipwright who can keep it safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There he goes again...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.35,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, on rare occasion, \Nhe gets straight to the point.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the best way! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then that's the plan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we find someone good!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And we need a musician, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.24,0:19:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just forget about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.32,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to be all excited, but have you forgotten what comes first?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.17,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get our gold back!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.71,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Question is, where's it hidden?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In a vault, most likely.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.65,0:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that! \NThe problem is, we don't know where it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.76,0:19:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't hafta yell at me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be here?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.93,0:20:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a guess, but if I were to hide gold in this fortress,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.97,0:20:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,this multi-lock storage vault \Nseems like the only place to do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.62,0:20:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so smart, Robin-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.02,0:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that does seem the most likely!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.44,0:20:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guys! \NLet's go there and get our gold back!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.93,0:20:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But are we just gonna leave the \NGoing Merry here? It'll get spotted!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.70,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hide a tree in a forest! Hide a ship in ships!"
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.38,0:20:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What, that's it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.31,0:20:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't try to get too serious that often.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.60,0:20:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the remains of a dock \Nwhere ships were built and repaired.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.77,0:20:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When we came in just now, \NI saw plenty of abandoned materials.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.19,0:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! I have a great idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.44,0:20:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whisper, whisper, whisper!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?! Help me out, guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadya think?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.10,0:21:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At least now we don't have to \Nworry about it being stolen again!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.72,0:21:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gluing paper all over the \NGoing Merry was a great idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.64,0:21:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I dunno how long it'll fool people,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.27,0:21:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,given how crappily it's been done...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.48,0:21:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! This is definitely a Navy warship, \Nno doubt about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.40,0:21:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.02,0:21:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You serious?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.23,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then! Now to get our gold back!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! We commence tonight at midnight! \NGot that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.16,0:21:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.16,0:21:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But why don't we go now?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.41,0:21:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause the mood'll be better at night, obviously!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Mood! I see!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think that's quite why.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.16,0:23:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we don't have to worry about Merry, \Nbut hold on, you guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.08,0:23:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just gonna go like this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.64,0:23:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! Seven people running \Naround will stand out too much!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.46,0:23:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! I'll give you my super secret plan!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.72,0:23:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next One Piece!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.26,0:23:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I do this part!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.30,0:23:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.59,0:23:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gold and Waver Recovery Operations!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.95,0:23:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be a brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.47,0:23:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?!
