Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:19.69,ED13-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Yume to iu mono oikakete ikou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:32.21,ED13-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Afure dashi teru subete no kotae ga kokoni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:38.75,ED13-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hashire, hashire, hiraka reta michi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:44.47,ED13-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Tomaru koto naku susumou, bokura wa dekiru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:50.56,ED13-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Makenai, makenai, ookina kabe demo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:23:00.15,ED13-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Kowagaru koto nante nai sa, norikoerareru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:11.60,ED13-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hurry up and get moving towards the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:19.69,ED13-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Let's move ahead, pursuing our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:32.21,ED13-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}All the answers are right here, pouring out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:38.75,ED13-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Rush forth, rush forth, on the road opened before us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:44.47,ED13-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's keep moving forward! We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:50.56,ED13-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fsp-0.15}We won't give in, we won't give in, even if the obstacle is big
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:23:00.15,ED13-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's nothing to be scared of, we can overcome it
